  <h4>How do we do it?</h4>
  <p>
    It's all about user experience (or simply UX), web standards, accessibility, proven web technologies and 
    agile development.
  </p>

  <p>
    Our creative team crafts beautiful web sites, making you feel good about the brand or service and 
    induce you to go with the flow and follow every line, image and link in an engaging way, that just makes you 
    want to <a href="contact.html">contact us</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Each application Gnomeslab produces puts the content and the user experience first, leading the end-user 
    in every step of the way. Then, when the stage is set, our talented technical pairs turn your ideas and 
    vision into an incredible software masterpiece.
  </p>

  <p>Iteration over iteration, with you in control, guiding our every move, your web application is nourished 
    and grows at a steady and predictable pace. With each iteration, a release that you can experiment and 
    make sure that it absolutely meets your needs.
  </p>

  <p>
    At Gnomeslab the project doesn't end when you sign the last check. Our masterpieces comes with a 12 month 
    support package, and warranty, that ensures us that bugs are not in your way when your web application 
    or product goes live.
  </p>
